        <item>
            <title>Samsung S25U 屏幕更襟跌？有片為證跌落測試 1 米以上仍生還屏幕無損</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/07/samsung-s25ultra-screen-more-durable-from-drop-test/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-s25ultra-screen-more-durable-from-drop-test</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/07/samsung-s25ultra-screen-more-durable-from-drop-test/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 07 Feb 2025 03:00:20 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Drop Test]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy S25 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[samsung]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1290414</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>對於不少手機用家來説，相信「用家最痛」肯定是手機跌落屏幕，雖説近年不少手機屏幕均更耐刮，但一旦不慎跌落石屎地，屏幕可以完美生還的手機在現今市場中亦確實不多。最近 Samsung 推出的旗艦手機 Galaxy S25 Ultra，就有外媒進行了跌落測試，結果確實有點驚喜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290416" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-1-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-1-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290417" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-2-694x384.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="384" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-2-694x384.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290418" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-3-694x385.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="385" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-3-694x385.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/samsungs25ultradropt-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>其實官方在發佈 Galaxy S25 Ultra 時已表明新機採用了全新，由 Corning 製造的新一代強化玻璃 Gorilla Armor 2 保護它的 6.9 吋 Dynamic AMOLED 2X 熒幕，雖然早前有外媒測試過它的耐刮程度不及上代 Galaxy S24 Ultra，但今日的跌落測試，測試者將 S25 Ultra 以不同角度從 1 米以上數次將 S25 Ultra 跌落石屎硬地，最後似乎也只是它的鈦金屬邊框有少許擦損，而熒幕在數次石屎硬地跌落測試後依然可以生還，而且更是完好無損，結果確實十分有驚喜。看來各位 S25 Ultra 的用家，最多也只需要入手玻璃貼加強防刮效果，對手機的防護應該已十分足夠了。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_64776"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/MivFjQOXQCM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>來源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MivFjQOXQCM&amp;t=267s">PBKreviews</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
