            <title>ASUS 推出金色版 RTX 5090，奢華設計瞄準中東市場</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/06/asus-rog-astral-rtx5090-gold/wireless-home/desktop-pc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=asus-rog-astral-rtx5090-gold</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/06/asus-rog-astral-rtx5090-gold/wireless-home/desktop-pc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 13:30:59 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[桌上電腦]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1290274</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>華碩（ASUS）近日發布 ROG Astral GeForce RTX 5090 Dhahab Gold Edition，這款顯示卡採用金色外觀與中東風格設計，展現該地區的繁榮與奢華。整體造型金碧輝煌，輔以祖母綠點綴細節，風扇軸心鑲嵌金色 ROG 標誌，背面更融入摩天大樓天際線，象徵中東城市從沙漠崛起，邁向現代化發展的歷程。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290275" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/psu-629x580.jpg" alt="" width="629" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/psu-629x580.jpg 629w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/psu.jpg 900w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 629px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://rog.asus.com/me-en/graphics-cards/graphics-cards/rog-astral/rog-astral-rtx5090-o32g-dhahab-edition/">ASUS</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290278" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pdback-694x397.png" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pdback-694x397.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pdback.png 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲背面刻有摩天大樓天際線，圖片來源：<a href="https://rog.asus.com/me-en/graphics-cards/graphics-cards/rog-astral/rog-astral-rtx5090-o32g-dhahab-edition/">ASUS</a></p><p>「Dhahab」在阿拉伯語中意為黃金，這款顯示卡外觀耀眼，細節亦精雕細琢。正面鑲刻阿拉伯書法，融入「力量、勇氣、團結」等字樣，展現當地文化底藴。框架採用全金屬壓鑄工藝，並搭載鍍金 GPU 支架，提升結構穩固度，亦增添尊貴感與耐用性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aura-694x568.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="568" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aura-694x568.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aura.jpg 912w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://rog.asus.com/me-en/graphics-cards/graphics-cards/rog-astral/rog-astral-rtx5090-o32g-dhahab-edition/">ASUS</a></p><p>技術規格方面，Dhahab Gold Edition 與標準版 ROG Astral RTX 5090 規格一致，採用四風扇散熱系統、均熱板導熱技術、高密度散熱鰭片，以及強化供電設計，確保運行效能穩定，發揮極致表現。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aura-694x568.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="568" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aura-694x568.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aura.jpg 912w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://rog.asus.com/me-en/graphics-cards/graphics-cards/rog-astral/rog-astral-rtx5090-o32g-dhahab-edition/">ASUS</a></p><p>華碩目前尚未公佈此特別版售價。標準版 RTX 5090 Astral 官方定價 3,079 美元（約港幣 23,978 元），市場普遍存在溢價，預計這款限量版 Dhahab Gold Edition 價格將再創新高。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290277" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pd-694x397.png" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pd-694x397.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/pd.png 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://rog.asus.com/me-en/graphics-cards/graphics-cards/rog-astral/rog-astral-rtx5090-o32g-dhahab-edition/">ASUS</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://rog.asus.com/me-en/graphics-cards/graphics-cards/rog-astral/rog-astral-rtx5090-o32g-dhahab-edition/">ASUS</a>、<a href="https://videocardz.com/newz/asus-unveils-rog-astral-geforce-rtx-5090-dhahab-gold-edition">Video Cardz</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/06/asus-rog-astral-rtx5090-gold/wireless-home/desktop-pc/">ASUS 推出金色版 RTX 5090，奢華設計瞄準中東市場</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
